                                          <Box name="Set Anti-Collision" id="4" localization="8" tooltip="Enable or disable the collision protection on some specific part of NAO&apos;s body.&#x0A;&#x0A;For example if the protection is enabled on his left arm he will move his arm all the&#x0A;same than when it is not but avoiding his other body parts." x="113" y="318">
